{"id":"e51307a2-3a0e-42ce-aef1-087ee94b4935","name":"Saint Seiya Myth Cloth Ex Action Figure Cygnus Hyoga (Final Bronze Cloth) 17cm (New)","slug":"saint-seiya-myth-cloth-ex-action-figure-","description":"<p><strong>Saint Seiya Myth Cloth </strong><b>Ex </b>Action Figure of <b>Cygnus Hyoga (Final Bronze Cloth)</b>, size approx.17cm. <strong>Official product</strong> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p>Seventeen years have passed since the <strong>Saint Cloth Myth Cygnus Hyoga (Final Bronze Cloth)</strong> was released. Now, this legendary hero joins <strong>Saint Cloth Myth EX</strong>! Redesigned to better capture the on-screen appearance of the character, it comes with numerous option parts and four optional expressions that can be used together with the EX <strong>Seiya</strong>, <strong>Shiryu</strong>, and <strong>Shun</strong> figures (each sold separately)!</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><strong>Content :</strong> </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Main Body</li>\n<li>Cloth armor set</li>\n<li>Object mode frame</li>\n<li>Three optional expressions</li>\n<li>Four pairs of optional hands,</li>\n<li>Aurora Execution hand option,</li>\n<li>Optional hair part set</li>\n<li>Optional chest par</li>\n<li>Four optional bonus expressions</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Box C10 condition (box are checked before sending).<br /><br />This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-04-06T11:26:45.162Z","updatedAt":"2025-04-06T11:26:45.162Z","barcode":"4573102650443","deletedAt":null,"source":"heo","hasFakeBarcode":false,"duplicateId":null,"brandId":"3a466736-f80f-4cbd-a1a0-d34efc302efd","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"e51307a2-3a0e-42ce-aef1-087ee94b4935","categoryId":"c6ea4121-907d-426e